Dialogue: 0.0:54:29.33.0:54:32.73.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(194.399)}- Wait. wait. wait. Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:32.80.0:54:33.89.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.400)}Shut the fuck up?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:33.97.0:54:36.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(202.400)}Don't play that shit with me.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:36.34.0:54:40.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(123.369)}I've always accepted you for who you are:
Dialogue: 0.0:54:36.34.0:54:40.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(177.400)}the good. the bad. and the ugly.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:40.14.0:54:43.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(175.369)}Don't tell me to shut the fuck up.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:40.14.0:54:43.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(118.400)}I'm not some parent you can treat like shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:43.34.0:54:46.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(173.369)}Well. good thing nobody's really
Dialogue: 0.0:54:43.34.0:54:46.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(155.400)}lookin' to you to be a fuckin' parent.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:47.08.0:54:49.05.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(269.397)}Yo! Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:50.92.0:54:52.44.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(293.397)}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:55.69.0:54:58.32.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(206.369)}When I sit across from you
Dialogue: 0.0:54:55.69.0:54:58.32.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(152.400)}and tell you somethin' about my life.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:58.42.0:55:00.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(125.400)}you don't get to use that shit against me.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:00.46.0:55:03.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(145.400)}You cross that line again. we're done.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:03.16.0:55:05.06.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(152.400)}You talk back right now. we're done.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:05.13.0:55:07.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(186.369)}One more fuckin' disrespectful
Dialogue: 0.0:55:05.13.0:55:07.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(225.400)}word outta your mouth.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:07.30.0:55:08.86.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(188.397)}and we're done. You hear me?
